%pyspark
import pandas as pd

data = pd.read_sql_table('sun_angle', conn)
data.head()

paragraphs.title: read pm mysql directly
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

pm_witlab = spark.read.format('jdbc').options(
        url='jdbc:mysql://localhost/pm_measure',
        driver='com.mysql.jdbc.Driver',
        dbtable='pm', user='pm_user', password='defacto8*'
    ).load()
    
pm_witlab.show()

%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import StringType

udf_minute = udf(lambda s: s.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M'), StringType())

pm_witlab.printSchema()

pw = pm_witlab.withColumn('datetime', udf_minute('datetime'))
pw.show()

%pyspark

from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
udf_dt = udf(lambda d, t: d + ' ' + t)

uv = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/uv_srs.parquet')
cld = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///dayday/clean_days.parquet')

uv_s = uv.withColumn('datetime', udf_dt('date', 'time'))\
         .select('datetime', 'uvb', 'euvb')

uvcl = uv.join(cld, 'date')
uvcl.show()

%sql
select datetime, euvb*100, pm10 from uvpm_w

paragraphs.title: uv clear day
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import (StringType, DoubleType)

udf_dh = udf(lambda s: s[:-3], StringType())
udf_joule = udf(lambda s: float(s)*60, DoubleType())

df_uv = uvcl.withColumn('datetime', udf_dt('date', 'time'))\
            .select('datetime', 'uvb', 'euvb', 'uvi')

uv_h = df_uv.withColumn('datehour', udf_dh('datetime')).drop('datetime')\
            .withColumn('uvb_j', udf_joule('uvb'))\
            .withColumn('euvb_j', udf_joule('euvb'))\
            .groupby('datehour').agg({'uvb_j': 'sum', 'euvb_j': 'sum', 'uvi': 'avg'})\
            .withColumnRenamed('sum(uvb_j)', 'sum_uvb')\
            .withColumnRenamed('sum(euvb_j)', 'sum_euvb')\
            .withColumnRenamed('avg(uvi)', 'avg_uvi')\

uv_h.show()

paragraphs.title: PM final
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

udf_pm_datetime_reformat = udf(lambda s: s[0:4] + '-' + s[4:6] + '-' + s[6:8]\
                                         + ' ' + s[8:])

pm_final = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///pm/airkorea/pm_final.parquet')
pm = pm_final.where('station_name = "성성동" or station_name = "성황동" or station_name = "백석동" or station_name = "성거읍"')\
             .select('datetime', 'pm10')\
             .withColumn('datehour', udf_pm_datetime_reformat('datetime'))\
             .drop('datetime')

pm.show()

paragraphs.title: classify grade
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

from pyjake.basemodule import udf_classifyPm10, udf_month, udf_weather
from pyspark.sql.types import (IntegerType)

def classifyPm10_2(pm):
    if 0 < pm <= 30:
        return 1
    elif 30 < pm <= 50:
        return 2
    elif 50 < pm <= 100:
        return 3
    elif pm > 100:
        return 4
    else:
        return 0
        
        
udf_classifyPm10_2 = udf(classifyPm10_2, IntegerType())
udf_classify_uv = udf(lambda u: int(u/1000), IntegerType())
udf_classify_uvi = udf(lambda u: int(u), IntegerType())
udf_classify_sza = udf(lambda s: int(s/10), IntegerType())

uvpmsza_group = uvpmsza.withColumn('uvb_g', udf_classify_uv('sum_uvb'))\
                       .withColumn('uvi_g', udf_classify_uvi('avg_uvi'))\
                       .withColumn('pm10_g', udf_classifyPm10_2('pm10'))\
                       .withColumn('sza_g', udf_classify_sza('solar_zenith'))\
                       .withColumn('month', udf_month('datehour'))\
                       .withColumn('weather', udf_weather('month'))\
                       .sort('datehour')

uvpmsza_group.show()
uvpmsza_group.createOrReplaceTempView('uvpmsza_group')
